#

Classic Clam Chowder

45 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

Comfort FoodSoupEasy

Description

A creamy and hearty clam chowder loaded with tender clams, potatoes, and a hint of smoky bacon.

Ingredients

  • chopped clams: 2 cans (6.5 oz each)
  • potatoes, diced: 2 cups
  • bacon, chopped: 4 slices
  • onion, diced: 1 medium
  • celery, diced: 1 cup
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • flour: 2 tablespoons
  • clam juice: 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • thyme, dried: 1 teaspoon
